Package org.sopra.api.exercises.exercise2

Interface Simplesort<T>

public interface Simplesort<T>
This interface models a simple sort algorithm for arrays of type <Simplesort>.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void simplesort​(T[] arr, int start, int end)
    This function sorts a given (unsorted) array by a simple sort algorithm within given left & right border.

  • Method Details

    • simplesort

      void simplesort​(T[] arr, int start, int end)
      This function sorts a given (unsorted) array by a simple sort algorithm within given left & right border. The array outside that borders stays untouched.
      Parameters:
      arr - Array of unsorted Elements <Simplesort>
      start - left border for iteration
      end - right border for iteration
